
Ranger Help for: enemy bear
===========================

SUMMARY:
Choosing bear means your Ranger is trained to bring down bears and
bear-like predators: heavy, clawed, territorial beasts that rely on bulk,
strength, and endurance.

This is a practical wilderness choice for forests, hills, mountains, arctic
lands, and caves where large predators roam.

COMMAND:
  setenemy bear

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: enemy, setenemy and terrains
